#
# supported targets
#   sparc.solaris8	SPARC sun4 Solaris8 target
#   x86.linux2.6	x86 linux2.6 (or linux 2.4 with NPTL) target
#
# supported builds
#   -dev      for development (not optimized, debug option on, symbolic debugging)
#   -test     for design based testing (high compiler Warning levels and coverage analysis)
#   -purify   for design based testing (for purification)
#   -release  for product release (optimized and no debugging info) and for requirement based testing
#
